messages.message:
Hi all, if your PRs are failing because of Cypress tests and these are the failing tests:
• field-editor.spec.ts - should filter fields and edit fields and classification correctly through field editor
• file-list.spec.ts - should test all file list functionality including displaying documents correctly, expand/collapse, and filters
• results-table.spec.ts - should have the correct counts and values and function correctly
• review-manager-dashboard.spec.ts - should do everything
• review-reviewer-dashboard.spec.ts - should do everything user can do
• run-app.spec.ts - runs the app
• run-public-app.spec.ts - runs the app
Basically, any test that is running an app. It is safe to force merge - we have a PR to revert the offending code (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/59724)
